com.koloboke.function

Interface DoubleCharConsumer


  • public interface DoubleCharConsumer
    Represents an operation that accepts a double-valued and a char-valued argument, and returns no result. This is the (double, char) specialization of BiConsumer. Unlike most other functional interfaces, DoubleCharConsumer is expected to operate via side-effects.
    See Also:
    BiConsumer
